reviewText: Very good informative teaching video, step by step instructions. I used it on my client and she loved it! Great for my chair massage routine also

Very happy with my purchase of this dvd. I have always been into learning different massaging techniques ever since I learned infant massage. This dvd came up when I searched for instructional massage and I am glad it did!  This dvd was very useful and I learned new tips that I had never thought of before.
I just found this DVD called Cool Head Massage techniques. Those tips helps me to massage that's why I love this DVD.
